> The menu can be **collapsed** by clicking the small arrow (◀) at the top right of the sidebar to give more screen space.

---

### 1.7 User Profile (Bottom Left)

At the bottom of the left menu, you will see the **logged-in user's profile**, displaying:

- Profile photo
- Username (e.g., *ADMIN*)
- Role (e.g., *ADMINISTRATOR*)

Click on this area to access profile settings or log out.

